name: email-templates
description: Skill dla tworzenia i testowania szablonów emaili (HTML i plain text) z podstawianiem zmiennych
topics:
  - templates
  - email
  - jinja2
  - testing
applyTo:
  - path: "**/templates/**"
  - path: "**/test_*templates*"
languageDetection:
  preferredLanguage: python
  patterns:
    - "template"
    - "render"